general.name: ssppOut_plate
general.description: This file contains the values of [Fe/H], log10 g, and Teff computed with various methods by the SSPP pipeline.
general.naming_convention: ssppOut-[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{5}\.fit, where [0-9]{4} is a 4-digit plate number, and [0-9]{5} is a 5-digit MJD.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
